title: 30k $CRE8R Tokens Budget For Vision, Branding & Marketing
body:
This proposal makes 30K CRE8R tokens available for a Coordinape circle.

The purpose of this is to bring all our creators together to discuss and work on documenting our vision and brand and then help more people understand who we are, what we do and how they can get involved. 

Lets work together and come up with a vision that we can all agree on, and be proud of. 

And then go share it with world. 

We already passed the proposal for 100k $CRE8R tokens budget we are applying for a share of that budget (not extra). 

10k per month distributed via coordinape. Anyone can join using the vouching system ( https://discourse.cre8r.vip/t/remove-content-filtering-system-replace-with-vouching-system/34 ).
